title: Anonymous Takes Down Egypt Government Websites to Protest Against Rabaa Massacre
text: Anonymous Rabaa, one of the group's Egyptian branches, has been attacking various government websites, defacing their frontpages to show messages in support of the August 2013 Rabaa Square massacre.
